gw.api.archiving.upgrade

Class IArchivedEntitySet

  • gw.api.archiving.upgrade.IArchivedEntitySet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<T>

    public class IArchivedEntitySet
implements Iterable<T>
    Represents a set of IArchivedEntity's for the same "old" entity type.
